{"tid":464814,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺養貓嘅女人9成9都精神病","createTime":"2017-11-11T01:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T02:10:07.000Z","uid":11779,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf93a1757a697ffbb8fa6a5f2537a11239c5567","tid":464814,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"我自己都有anxiety，hallucination 同 depression, 但睇到班貓膠覺得佢地仲痴線過我.<br />\n<br />\n我地有病都會去認去改去接受自己嘅缺陷 講野前會諗一諗先，但班貓膠 唔理3721乜都屌左先 又屈人賣狗肉 又話間野有黑社會做後台又話警察偏幫佢地 到比人証實係羊就個個潛晒水，當日有份屌間小店嘅人連一句對唔住都冇講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成9日對住隻貓主人前主人後 我都懷疑佢地會唔會同隻貓扑野，屌 真係好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69e0a3e091c2cffcf7311e62754928ba067b008","tid":464814,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa20637f1e50cf4cb287ab47599d906f7f2469e","tid":464814,"uid":68904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:59:26.000Z","msg":"唔覺 我媽咪唔比我養猫但佢都係有精神病<br />\n<br />\n申行：有精神病"},{"pid":"b13ba791f4f7b1229e7d83a99aca8761b8e8f867","tid":464814,"uid":151877,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"會同貓扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓閪真係好緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 養貓"},{"pid":"17f540127eb12069fe0b619136ce9918ef1295c6","tid":464814,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"狗膠先屈人賣狗肉喎ching"},{"pid":"9da190eb9f4a271d218e3911b9a4292fc0744c60","tid":464814,"uid":144,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img